snippet.title: Five Shows at Wario's - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Join my Discord: https://discord.gg/Sabb6hH

Five Shows at Wario's is the latest FNAW game. It will play very differently than any of the previous FNAW game (and probably any FNAF game). The game is going very well, and at the time of this being uploaded, I'd say the game is about 30% complete. I want this to be the biggest FNAW game to date, without simply adding content for the sake of quantity.

Perhaps you wonder: Where are we? Who are we playing as? Where does this fit in the storyline? All of this will be answered soon enough...
